overview:
YouEtch.com is a Canadian company operating from Ottawa, Ontario, Canada. At YouEtch.com we provide laser engraved products and services to both sectors at the consumer level and corporate level. We specialize in what we call ‘Permanent Art’, we transform products like iPhone cases, Dog-tags, Aluminum business cards, wood business cards, money clips, and more from ordinary products to permanent top of the line personalized items.

Unlike stickers & skins our products are laser-etched, so say goodbye to the sticky tape or edges that can rise up and peel off. We laser etch (tattoo) the artwork & text directly into the surface of the cases, which ensures a lasting effect. In other words no matter how you use or abuse the covers the etched art will always be there. Visit YouEtch.com for more information.
